node.text:
I visited back home to Detroit a couple weeks ago and I was able to surprise my Mom with an advance copy of our #LeapOfFaithBook and catch her reaction! She was also pleasantly surprised by our book dedication 😌💕📚✨Love you Momma! ✨💕 Moments like this make all the hard work have purpose! 💕 if you haven’t already click the link in my bio to grab your copy! ✨📚

#LeapIfFaithBook OUT NOW! 💫

node.text: Yesterday was so magical! Shoutout to all of the beautiful souls who attended our book signing at @eagleeyebooks! I’m so grateful for our extended fam! You honestly touched my heart more than you know with all of your love, support, stories and positivity! Sharing so much of our life is scary at times…But moments like yesterday make it all worth it! All of the books sold out of the store except a few and my heart is full! I didn’t know if 2 people where gonna show or 50 but by the end it was standing room only! I’m tearing up writing this because I’m just so grateful! Thank you all again and I hope to keep making y’all proud ❤️ #LeapOfFaithBook available now!

WIN @SmartSweets Candy! 🍭 🍬🍭🍬
 
I LOVE candy! That’s why I’m so excited to team up with @SmartSweets for a sweet giveaway of a month’s supply of #KickSugar candy!🤤
 
I love snacking on my #SmartSweets when I’m kicked back watching Netflix! My personal favorites are the Gummy Worms and Lollipops ✨😋 but they offer 8 delicious candy flavors you know and love (AKA feel good versions of traditional candy). PLUS they're up to 92% less sugar than traditional candy and DELICIOUS! These treats are rich in fiber, gluten free and low calorie! 
 
So here’s how you enter ⬇️:
🍬Follow @SmartSweets
🍬 Like this post
🍬Tag up to 10 friends in the comments! (1 comment + tag = 1 entry!)
🍬 Must be a US or CAD Resident to enter
⚡Also use my code LAUREN15 for 15% off orders of $30+! ⚡
